== Description ==
Plug & Play is a cross-platform WordPress library of elements for building an <strong>Elegant and Secure</strong> WordPress web site. <strong>Plug and Play</strong> our feautures for WordPress to Turn your WordPress Blog into a Highly Interactive Blog.

[Read more](https://wordpress.org/plugins/plug-and-play/) about with this plugin!

<h4>Features</h4> 
* Hide Admin Bar
* WP Generator Meta Tag Remover
* Security Tools 
* Versus

